    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Henri and the Hexagons is a top-down narrative adventure game where you play as Henri, a grumpy old man, and his loyal canine companion, both represented by simple dots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the minimalist aesthetic of Martin Panchaud, the 2023 Angoulême Comics Festival Grand Prize winner, Henri and the Hexagons invites players to project their own imagination onto each scene.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Behind this minimalist appearance hides a fantastical and humorous world filled with bizarre characters and outlandish situations. For Henri, a grumpy sixty-year-old based in Switzerland, could unwittingly become the savior of the Earth and traverse multiple solar systems. Embark on increasingly extravagant quests like in RPGs, pilot top-secret vehicles in shoot-'em-up style... Henri and the Hexagons is also a tribute to the great classics of video games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Aesthetic</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a unique world where all characters are represented by simple geometric shapes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/c64b6330e1ebbf0de33fa927057100b2.poster.avif?t=1728657362\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/c64b6330e1ebbf0de33fa927057100b2.webm?t=1728657362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/c64b6330e1ebbf0de33fa927057100b2.mp4?t=1728657362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Surprising Gameplays</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow Henri's adventures and enjoy a variety of gameplay elements, each seamlessly integrated into the narrative. From classic RPGs to shoot 'em ups, players will always be surprised!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/d08c7a62263b164ebfacb2cfd063e7ee.poster.avif?t=1728657362\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/d08c7a62263b164ebfacb2cfd063e7ee.webm?t=1728657362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/d08c7a62263b164ebfacb2cfd063e7ee.mp4?t=1728657362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Touching Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The adventures of this anti-hero oscillate between the grotesque and more serious moments, exploring themes such as old age and family relationships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/4e29377c4f76993df3a0ebeee57e08ea.poster.avif?t=1728657362\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/4e29377c4f76993df3a0ebeee57e08ea.webm?t=1728657362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268480/extras/4e29377c4f76993df3a0ebeee57e08ea.mp4?t=1728657362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Henri and his dog on their extraordinary cosmic odyssey!</p>",
